<div class="scp-image-caption" style="width:500px;">
<p>Even an Awaktoid can read this map. We won't baby you!</p>
</div>
</div>
<p><span style="font-size:1.2em;"><br />
We plan on annihilating the cities highlighted in red. Behind one of them may be the key to freedom.</span></p>
